# 🤖 AI Assignment Tracker (Prompt Engineering Project)

🚀 Live Demo: https://smart-solid-study-flow.base44.app

---

## 🧠 Overview

This project focuses on designing and structuring **effective prompts** to build an AI-powered Assignment Tracker using a no-code platform (Base44).
The system enables teachers to generate assignments using AI and students to interact with them through a structured workflow.

---

## 🎯 Objective

To design a prompt-driven system that:

* Generates assignments using AI
* Converts them into structured PDFs
* Enables student submissions
* Evaluates responses using AI
* Generates feedback reports

---

## ⚙️ Prompt Engineering Highlights

### 1. Assignment Generation Prompt

* Generates subject-specific MCQs
* Ensures structured output
* Converts output → PDF → auto-assigned to students

### 2. Evaluation Prompt

* Analyzes student submissions
* Classifies performance:

  * Good
  * Satisfactory
  * Bad
* Generates detailed feedback
* Converts feedback → downloadable PDF for students

### 3. Workflow Automation

* AI-generated assignments automatically:

  * Converted to PDF
  * Uploaded
  * Reflected on student dashboard

---

## 🔄 System Flow

1. Teacher generates assignment via AI
2. AI creates questions → converted to PDF
3. Assignment auto-uploaded to student dashboard
4. Student downloads, completes, uploads
5. AI evaluates submission
6. Feedback generated → shown & downloadable as PDF

---

## ✨ Features

* AI-based assignment generation
* Automated PDF creation & distribution
* AI-based evaluation & feedback
* Student & Teacher dashboards
* Deadline tracking with priority indicators
* Clean and responsive UI

---

## 🛠 Platform Used

* Base44 (No-code AI platform)

